    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >OVR Locomotion Effect 是一款旨在减轻 VR（运动）眩晕的覆盖工具。它会在拇指摇杆输入时向头显显示舒适的效果。你可以在所有 SteamVR 游戏中使用该效果。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >免费体验版</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>我们建议你在购买前先尝试体验版。</strong> 它功能完整，但每次试用都有时间限制。它应该与库中的任何 VR 游戏兼容。看看它是否能帮助你减少 VR 眩晕。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[<br>&quot;][/url] </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >通过拇指摇杆输入的防眩晕效果</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393780/extras/3f0b516797efe30f88181e1017f38c27.poster.avif?t=1757680865\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393780/extras/3f0b516797efe30f88181e1017f38c27.webm?t=1757680865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393780/extras/3f0b516797efe30f88181e1017f38c27.mp4?t=1757680865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据你的控制输入，在头显上显示减轻 VR 眩晕的效果。完成初始设置后，该效果可应用于任何 SteamVR 游戏。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >仪表盘设置</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393780/extras/c0d140b00c055eb3597db14efc4c9839.poster.avif?t=1757680865\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393780/extras/c0d140b00c055eb3597db14efc4c9839.webm?t=1757680865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393780/extras/c0d140b00c055eb3597db14efc4c9839.mp4?t=1757680865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 SteamVR 仪表盘上快速调整效果。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多种效果</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393780/extras/6cf3421c35519ad2f8401fbcc9093870.poster.avif?t=1757680865\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393780/extras/6cf3421c35519ad2f8401fbcc9093870.webm?t=1757680865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393780/extras/6cf3421c35519ad2f8401fbcc9093870.mp4?t=1757680865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提供暗角、房间、点和风的效果。这些效果可以组合使用。你可以将其调整到几乎不可见，或者覆盖大部分视野。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏手柄</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393780/extras/7c2b4ce69f402f25da0fd655c9d333ca.poster.avif?t=1757680865\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393780/extras/7c2b4ce69f402f25da0fd655c9d333ca.webm?t=1757680865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393780/extras/7c2b4ce69f402f25da0fd655c9d333ca.mp4?t=1757680865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持游戏手柄。摆脱来自 VR 模组的眩晕。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >用户指南、常见问题、错误报告和需求</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请查看本页面右侧菜单中的论坛（讨论）页面。你可以从论坛或 Discord 服务器获得支持。</p>",
